\is1 Introduction
\ip Seini ka igkarangeb sulat of Apustul John the sabeka te followers of Jesus. Impeendiye din ka seini sulat te woman in-alam te God and diye degma te me anak din. Ne kema ke punduk buwa te migmalintutuu ka igpasabut din kayi. Seini se malepet sulat, mighangyu te keilangan eg-ikul te kamalehetan and egpaheyinaweey ka tagse sabeka, and migpaney-paney degma seini concerning the people migpanulu ware kun migpekeetew si Hisu Kristu.
